Package com.leantegra.wibeat.sdk.monitoring.listeners

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BackgroundScanServiceConsumer
    The interface is used in BackgroundScanManager and provides callbacks indicating whether the service connection state has changed.
    ChangeGlobalConfigListener  
    MonitoringListener
    Callback to be triggered when WiBeats are discovered in a region.
    RangingListener
    Callback to be triggered when WiBeats are ranged.
    RawScanListener
    Callback interface is used to deliver LE scan results.
    ScanListener
    Bluetooth LE scan callbacks.
    ScanServiceConsumer
    The interface is used in ScanServiceManager and provides callbacks indicating whether the service connection state has changed.
    WiBeatMonitoringListener
    Callback to be triggered when the proximity zone changed for the monitored WiBeat.
